⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Sam Flynn
node TRN · TRN · ⟦Sam Flynn:TRN:9652b2⟧

WHO   — Sam Flynn — the heir · the User who went in
WHAT  — The way-in of the 2010 film: a User of the next generation who enters to find his lost father and the world he built.
WHERE — TRN · TRON  Framework inputs: TRON (Disney, 1982–2025)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the saga needed an inheritor — a User born after the Grid, who must decide what to do with his father's legacy.
HOW   — By a motorcyclist's nerve, his father's code in his blood, and a willingness to be digitized after him.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  My father went in and never came home; I followed him onto the Grid, and brought back the one miracle he couldn't save.

